1
00:00:01,000 --> 00:00:04,500
THE INTERN: Good morning everyone!
I have exciting news about
the subtitle project!

2
00:00:05,000 --> 00:00:09,200
ALEX: Please tell me you didn't
convert all the files to
a format nobody uses.

3
00:00:09,800 --> 00:00:13,000
THE INTERN: I converted them
all to Comic Sans.

4
00:00:13,500 --> 00:00:16,800
ALEX: Comic Sans is a font,
not a subtitle format.

5
00:00:17,200 --> 00:00:21,500
THE INTERN: That explains why
the video player kept
crashing, I suppose.

6
00:00:22,000 --> 00:00:26,200
JORDAN: Just use ConvertICO next time.
It literally tells you
what formats are supported.

7
00:00:26,800 --> 00:00:30,500
THE INTERN: But where's the adventure
in doing things the easy way?

8
00:00:31,000 --> 00:00:34,000
ALEX: The adventure is in keeping
your job, that's where.
